{"tid":869411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實龍心只係個冇包袱, IQ正常既人","createTime":"2018-10-20T10:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T20:07:40.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e4c84a563e9babde8189658e27fd3fb2723d224","tid":869411,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"佢冇家人呢個包袱<br />\n亦冇怕留案底既包袱 <br />\n亦冇供樓既包袱 <br />\n<br />\n佢浸過咸水<br />\n或多或少都受到外國文化嘅影響<br />\n佢其實一直係探索緊人生既意義 <br />\n佢會去質疑「何謂Freedom? 何謂自由？」<br />\n佢一直就係透過行動去探索呢啲open question <br />\n<br />\n旁人會覺得佢嘅行為好傻<br />\n因為普羅大眾有好多嘅包袱<br />\n會克制自己行為<br />\n所以會覺得龍心做嘅嘢係「不正常」<br />\n<br />\n龍心眼下嘅我哋<br />\n亦都係「不正常」<br />\n<br />\n其實<br />\n龍心只係一個冇包袱<br />\nIQ正常既人<br />\n佢所做嘅<br />\n只係一場學術上嘅探索"},{"pid":"cd4310e53a63952ffa1c737602e44880cd49c46a","tid":869411,"uid":187108,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"又吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccf2225dd91243e0d30580982c56a0b2d8c7a0b2","tid":869411,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"搞精神病人點計"},{"pid":"c130bf34f46a0b73d5d30f5ce9a7c3a1733f8089","tid":869411,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ccf2225dd91243e0d30580982c56a0b2d8c7a0b2","tid":869411,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"搞精神病人點計"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"龍心行緊大蛇丸果條路"},{"pid":"9073907e9a0132538b8b93caf629cdfcc9f8c4ee","tid":869411,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T18:36:45.000Z","msg":"只不過係一個有錢既馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"394dee5808f895d3664077203cce67273991a1b7","tid":869411,"uid":49812,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9073907e9a0132538b8b93caf629cdfcc9f8c4ee","tid":869411,"uid":20584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re